http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/Minister-hails-contribution-of-Navodaya-Vidyalayas/article14016579.ece

Union Minister of State Human Resource Development Upendra Kushwaha has stated that the Centre would spare no effort in the progress of Navodaya Vidyalayas as modern destinations of learning in school education. Speaking at the inaugural ceremony of the two-day Navodaya National Integration meet here on Saturday, the Minister said students who were making it to Navodaya Vidyalaya were fortunate to have the kind of education system of making them responsible citizens, as very few educational institutions, even in private sector, have such infrastructure.